{
  "info": {
    "name": "dcm4chee-arc 5.x API",
    "description": "DICOMweb REST API untuk dcm4chee-arc-light 5.x\n\n## Setup\n1. Import collection ini ke Postman\n2. Set variable `host` (default: `{{host}}`)\n3. SSL verification OFF (Settings > SSL certificate verification = OFF)\n4. Klik \"Get Access Token\" dulu untuk ambil token\n5. Token otomatis terisi ke header Authorization via pre-request script\n\n## Auto Token (Pre-request Script)\nCollection ini memiliki pre-request script yang:\n- Cek apakah token sudah expired\n- Ambil token baru via Keycloak jika perlu\n- Set header `Authorization: Bearer {token}` otomatis\n\nToken berlaku 300 detik (5 menit). Script akan refresh otomatis.\n\nBase URL: `https://{{host}}:8443/dcm4chee-arc/aets/DCM4CHEE/rs`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "dcm4chee-guidelines"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "host",
      "value": "{{host}}",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "base",
      "value": "https://{{host}}:8443/dcm4chee-arc/aets/DCM4CHEE/rs",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "keycloak_url",
      "value": "https://{{host}}:8843",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token_expiry",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "study_uid",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "series_uid",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "instance_uid",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "exec": [
          "// ==================================================",
          "// Pre-request Script: Auto Token Management",
          "// ==================================================",
          "// Ambil token dari variable environment",
          "const token = pm.variables.get('token');",
          "const expiryStr = pm.variables.get('token_expiry');",
          "",
          "// Fungsi untuk ambil token baru",
          "function getNewToken() {",
          "    const keycloakUrl = pm.variables.get('keycloak_url');",
          "    const host = pm.variables.get('host');",
          "",
          "    if (!keycloakUrl || keycloakUrl === 'https://{{host}}:8843') {",
          "        pm.variables.set('keycloak_url', `https://${host}:8843`);",
          "    }",
          "",
          "    const tokenUrl = `${pm.variables.get('keycloak_url')}/realms/dcm4che/protocol/openid-connect/token`;",
          "",
          "    console.log(`[Token] Ambil token baru dari: ${tokenUrl}`);",
          "",
          "    pm.sendRequest({",
          "        url: tokenUrl,",
          "        method: 'POST',",
          "        header: {",
          "            'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded'",
          "        },",
          "        body: {",
          "            mode: 'urlencoded',",
          "            urlencoded: [",
          "                { key: 'client_id', value: 'dcm4chee-arc-rs' },",
          "                { key: 'client_secret', value: 'changeit' },",
          "                { key: 'username', value: 'admin' },",
          "                { key: 'password', value: 'changeit' },",
          "                { key: 'grant_type', value: 'password' }",
          "            ]",
          "        }",
          "    }, function (err, res) {",
          "        if (err) {",
          "            console.error('[Token] Gagal ambil token:', err);",
          "            return;",
          "        }",
          "",
          "        if (res.code >= 400) {",
          "            console.error('[Token] Error response:', res.code, res.text());",
          "            return;",
          "        }",
          "",
          "        try {",
          "            const json = res.json();",
          "            const newToken = json.access_token;",
          "            const expiresIn = json.expires_in || 300;",
          "",
          "            // Simpan token dan waktu expiry",
          "            pm.variables.set('token', newToken);",
          "            pm.variables.set('token_expiry', String(Date.now() + (expiresIn * 1000)));",
          "",
          "            console.log(`[Token] Token baru didapat, berlaku ${expiresIn} detik`);",
          "        } catch (e) {",
          "            console.error('[Token] Gagal parse response:', e);",
          "        }",
          "    });",
          "}",
          "",
          "// Cek apakah perlu ambil token baru",
          "if (!token || !expiryStr) {",
          "    console.log('[Token] Token belum ada, ambil baru...');",
          "    getNewToken();",
          "} else {",
          "    const expiry = parseInt(expiryStr, 10);",
          "    // Refresh jika sisa waktu < 30 detik",
          "    if (Date.now() > (expiry - 30000)) {",
          "        console.log('[Token] Token mau expired, refresh...');",
          "        getNewToken();",
          "    } else {",
          "        console.log('[Token] Token masih valid');",
          "    }",
          "}",
          "",
          "// Set header Authorization (akan terisi setelah async request selesai)",
          "if (pm.variables.get('token')) {",
          "    pm.request.headers.add({",
          "        key: 'Authorization',",
          "        value: `Bearer ${pm.variables.get('token')}`",
          "    });",
          "}"
        ],
        "type": "text/javascript"
      }
    },
    {
      "listen": "test",
      "script": {
        "exec": [
          "// ==================================================",
          "// Test Script: Simpan UID dari response ke variable",
          "// ==================================================",
          "// Kalau status 200 dan response JSON, simpan study_uid pertama",
          "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
          "    try {",
          "        const json = pm.response.json();",
          "        if (Array.isArray(json) && json.length > 0) {",
          "            // Simpan StudyInstanceUID",
          "            const study = json[0];",
          "            if (study['0020000D'] && study['0020000D'].Value) {",
          "                pm.variables.set('study_uid', study['0020000D'].Value[0]);",
          "                console.log('[Test] Study UID:', study['0020000D'].Value[0]);",
          "            }",
          "            // Simpan SeriesInstanceUID",
          "            if (study['0020000E'] && study['0020000E'].Value) {",
          "                pm.variables.set('series_uid', study['0020000E'].Value[0]);",
          "                console.log('[Test] Series UID:', study['0020000E'].Value[0]);",
          "            }",
          "            // Simpan SOPInstanceUID",
          "            if (study['00080018'] && study['00080018'].Value) {",
          "                pm.variables.set('instance_uid', study['00080018'].Value[0]);",
          "                console.log('[Test] Instance UID:', study['00080018'].Value[0]);",
          "            }",
          "        }",
          "    } catch (e) {",
          "        console.log('[Test] Bukan JSON response');",
          "    }",
          "}",
          "",
          "// Kalau error, tampilkan info",
          "if (pm.response.code >= 400) {",
          "    console.error('[Test] Error:', pm.response.code, pm.response.text().substring(0, 200));",
          "}"
        ],
        "type": "text/javascript"
      }
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Endpoint autentikasi Keycloak",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Access Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.access_token) {",
                  "    pm.variables.set('token', json.access_token);",
                  "    const expiresIn = json.expires_in || 300;",
                  "    pm.variables.set('token_expiry', String(Date.now() + (expiresIn * 1000)));",
                  "    console.log('[Test] Token tersimpan, berlaku ' + expiresIn + ' detik');",
                  "    ",
                  "    // Auto-set collection variable",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.access_token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "urlencoded",
              "urlencoded": [
                {
                  "key": "client_id",
                  "value": "dcm4chee-arc-rs",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "client_secret",
                  "value": "changeit",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "username",
                  "value": "admin",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "password",
                  "value": "changeit",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "grant_type",
                  "value": "password",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{keycloak_url}}/realms/dcm4che/protocol/openid-connect/token",
              "host": ["{{keycloak_url}}"],
              "path": ["realms", "dcm4che", "protocol", "openid-connect", "token"]
            },
            "description": "Ambil access token dari Keycloak.\n\nResponse akan menyimpan token ke variable `token` dan `token_expiry` secara otomatis."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "QIDO-RS (Query)",
      "description": "Query DICOM objects (Studies, Series, Instances)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Search Studies",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/dicom+json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base}}/studies?limit=20",
              "host": ["{{base}}"],
              "path": ["studies"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "limit", "value": "20" },
                { "key": "offset", "value": "0", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "PatientName", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "PatientID", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "StudyDate", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "ModalitiesInStudy", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "StudyDescription", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "AccessionNumber", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "includefield", "value": "all", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "fuzzymatching", "value": "true", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Cari studies dengan filter optional.\n\nParameter query:\n- `PatientName` : Wildcard dengan `*` (contoh: `Smit*`)\n- `StudyDate` : Tanggal (`20250115`) atau rentang (`20250101-20250131`)\n- `ModalitiesInStudy` : Filter modalitas (`CT`, `MR`, `DX`, dll)\n- `limit` : Jumlah maksimal hasil (default: 50)\n- `offset` : Halaman"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Search Series",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/dicom+json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base}}/studies/{{study_uid}}/series",
              "host": ["{{base}}"],
              "path": ["studies", "{{study_uid}}", "series"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "Modality", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "SeriesDescription", "value": "", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Cari series dalam study tertentu.\n\n`study_uid` akan terisi otomatis dari response Search Studies."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Search Instances",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/dicom+json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base}}/studies/{{study_uid}}/series/{{series_uid}}/instances",
              "host": ["{{base}}"],
              "path": ["studies", "{{study_uid}}", "series", "{{series_uid}}", "instances"]
            },
            "description": "Cari instance dalam series tertentu.\n\n`study_uid` dan `series_uid` akan terisi otomatis dari response Search Studies / Search Series."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "WADO-RS (Retrieve)",
      "description": "Retrieve DICOM objects, metadata, dan rendered images",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Study Metadata",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/dicom+json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base}}/studies/{{study_uid}}/metadata",
              "host": ["{{base}}"],
              "path": ["studies", "{{study_uid}}", "metadata"]
            },
            "description": "Ambil metadata semua instance dalam study (tanpa pixel data).\n\nResponse: JSON array of DICOM objects."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Series Metadata",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/dicom+json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base}}/studies/{{study_uid}}/series/{{series_uid}}/metadata",
              "host": ["{{base}}"],
              "path": ["studies", "{{study_uid}}", "series", "{{series_uid}}", "metadata"]
            },
            "description": "Ambil metadata instance dalam series tertentu."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Instance Metadata",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/dicom+json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base}}/studies/{{study_uid}}/series/{{series_uid}}/instances/{{instance_uid}}/metadata",
              "host": ["{{base}}"],
              "path": ["studies", "{{study_uid}}", "series", "{{series_uid}}", "instances", "{{instance_uid}}", "metadata"]
