              "path": ["studies", "{{study_uid}}", "series", "{{series_uid}}", "instances", "{{instance_uid}}"]
            },
            "description": "Download satu file DICOM.\n\n> **Catatan:** Gunakan `Accept: multipart/related; type=\"application/dicom\"` (bukan `application/dicom`).\n\nKlik \"Send and Download\" untuk menyimpan file."
          }
